        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "E5.2各加2mL乙酸缓冲液，0.4mL乙酰乙酸乙酯，混匀，于沸水浴中朋热1Umn，出传王王m。",
        "bbox": [
          0.13247863247863248,
          0.4595082122851989,
          0.875,
          0.47545808411658597
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "E5.3各加4mL乙酸乙酯，加塞振摇50次，离心5min，取出静置分层。",
        "bbox": [
          0.12606837606837606,
          0.46482483622899456,
          0.8707264957264957,
          0.4948257856261274
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "E5.4各取2mL乙酸乙酯萃取液，于另外6支10mL具塞比色管中，各加改良显色剂2mL，加塞振 摇，静置10min。",
        "bbox": [
          0.12713675213675213,
          0.49634482103864047,
          0.8979700854700855,
          0.5343207063514668
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "E5.5用比色皿在波长553nm（或绿色滤光片）下，以乙酸乙酯作参比，测得各标准管吸光度。",
        "bbox": [
          0.12980769230769232,
          0.5343207063514668,
          0.8269230769230769,
          0.5498908193297256
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "E5.6以吸光度（扣除空白吸光度)为纵坐标，δ-ALA量为横坐标，在坐标纸上绘制标准曲线。",
        "bbox": [
          0.13194444444444445,
          0.5525491313016234,
          0.8242521367521367,
          0.5692585208392671
        ],
        "order": 14
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "样品管吸光度减去尿空白管吸光度，查标准曲线得样品管中δ-ALA含量(μmoi（ug）〕。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1597222222222222,
          0.6076141650052217,
          0.7922008547008547,
          0.6247033133959935
        ],
        "order": 16
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "a．乙酸乙酯、乙酰乙酸乙酯最好为近期产品。改良显色剂宜新鲜配制；",
        "bbox": [
          0.16826923076923078,
          0.6964777366372353,
          0.7077991452991453,
          0.7128073673217507
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_18",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "b. 加入显色剂后，应静置10min，比色应在30min内完成； c. 尿液易腐败，可导致pH升高，影响测定结果。如不能及时测定，应将尿液保存在冰箱中； d. 其他与对二甲氨基苯甲醛显色剂反应的阳性物质，由于不被乙酸乙酯萃取，故不干扰测定； e. 测定尿样时，可同时做标准测定（取2mL标准应用液）。",
        "bbox": [
          0.16613247863247863,
          0.7143264027342637,
          0.8771367521367521,
          0.7872401025348903
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_19",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "计算：",
